rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0001
rows.name:
It's a good thing we avoided a war!
It would have been terrible if it had happened!

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0002
rows.name:
If relations between countries sour,
trade stagnates, and my wood products
won't sell!

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I want people all over Alst to know the
wonder of Gulan wood products!

rows.label: tlk41400021_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It would be very sad if I couldn't achieve that
because of a war!
